 ('11', '34', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"subhead water\">Two Thirds with Gutter</p>\n\n<p>This component gives you two columns to work with. The first taking up about two thirds the width of available content area. Most of your content would go here. As with other components, you have the WYSIWYG editor which will allow you to pick and choose your font styles.</p>', '<p class=\"subhead water\">Component</p>\n\n<p>The second column only takes up a third of the width of available content area. It should be used for smaller bits of information.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-08-05 19:11:16', '2016-08-09 21:31:00', 'b967f359-2246-4d0f-9050-a168526ff8cf'),
